";}s:36:"_service_details_card_1_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e60f1bb8f";}s:33:"service_details_card_2_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:16:"Patent Services:";}s:34:"_service_details_card_2_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e6031bb8e";}s:35:"service_details_card_2_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:419:"If you have an invention or innovative technology, our team can assist with patent protection. We provide strategic counsel on patentability, conduct patent searches, and draft and file patent applications. Our lawyers have experience in various industries and can effectively handle the complexities of the patent process. We also assist with patent portfolio management and enforcement to protect your inventions.

";}s:36:"_service_details_card_2_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e60f1bb8f";}s:33:"service_details_card_3_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:24:"Trade Secret Protection:";}s:34:"_service_details_card_3_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e6031bb8e";}s:35:"service_details_card_3_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:390:"We understand the value of trade secrets in maintaining a competitive edge. Our lawyers can help you identify and protect your trade secrets through comprehensive strategies, including confidentiality agreements, non-disclosure agreements (NDAs), and internal policies to safeguard sensitive information. We also provide guidance on trade secret enforcement and litigation if necessary.

